<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>
  <meta name="description"
    content="Tana Music Fiji — Premium island recording studio in Fiji. Head producer Harry Levy delivers world-class music production, vocal tracking, mixing, and mastering rooted in Pacific soul.">
  <meta name="keywords"
    content="Tana Music, Fiji, recording studio, music production, Harry Levy, mixing, mastering, Pacific music">
  <meta name="author" content="Tana Music Fiji">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Tana Music Fiji — The Pulse of Fijian Sound">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Global production standards rooted in Pacific soul. Directed by Harry Levy.">
  <meta property="og:image" content="/images/hero-studio.jpeg">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <link rel="icon" href="/images/tana-logo.jpeg" type="image/jpeg">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       NAVIGATION
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <nav class="nav" id="navbar">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
        <img src="/images/tana-logo.jpeg" alt="Tana Music Logo">
        <span>TANA MUSIC</span>
      </a>
      <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="#gallery">The Lab</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Book a Session</a></li>
      </ul>
      <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO SECTION
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="hero" id="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/hero-studio.jpeg" alt="Tana Music Studio - Recording Setup">
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        Fiji's Premier Studio
      </div>
      <h1>The <span class="accent">Pulse</span> of Fijian Sound.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Global production standards rooted in Pacific soul.<br>Directed by <strong>Harry
          Levy</strong>.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <polygon points="10,8 16,12 10,16" />
          </svg>
          Start Your Project
        </a>
        <a href="#about" class="btn-ghost">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12" />
            <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8" />
          </svg>
          Learn More
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       ABOUT / THE PRODUCER
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section about" id="about">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-image reveal">
          <img src="/images/harry-mic.jpeg" alt="Harry Levy - Head Producer at Tana Music Fiji">
          <div class="image-accent"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-text">
          <div class="reveal">
            <span class="section-label">The Producer</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">Harry Levy</h2>
            <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Fiji's premier sound engineer with a global ear and
              island soul.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <p>With <strong>over 15 years of relentless craft</strong>, Harry Levy has established himself as Fiji's
              most sought-after music producer and sound engineer. From the raw energy of a live session to the surgical
              precision of a final master, Harry brings an uncompromising standard to every project that passes through
              Tana Music.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <p>Specializing in <strong>vocal tracking, mixing, and mastering</strong>, he has shaped the sound of
              countless Pacific artists—blending the warmth of island rhythms with the polish of international
              production. His studio is a crucible where raw talent meets world-class engineering.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <p>Whether it's a reggae anthem destined for Spotify or a soulful ballad for Apple Music, Harry's ears
              deliver a sonic signature that is unmistakably <strong>Tana</strong>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stats reveal reveal-delay-4">
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">15+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Years Experience</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Tracks Produced</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Artists Mixed</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       SERVICES
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section services" id="services">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="services-header reveal">
        <span class="section-label" style="justify-content: center;">What We Do</span>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: center;">The Services</h2>
        <p class="section-desc" style="text-align: center;">End-to-end music production for artists who demand
          excellence. From the first note to the final master.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <!-- Card 1: Production -->
        <div class="service-card reveal">
          <div class="service-icon">🎹</div>
          <h3>Production</h3>
          <p>From raw demo to full arrangement. We sculpt your ideas into polished, radio-ready compositions with
            meticulous attention to detail.</p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20,6 9,17 4,12" />
              </svg>
              Full beat production & arrangement
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20,6 9,17 4,12" />
              </svg>
              Live instrument integration
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20,6 9,17 4,12" />
              </svg>
              Songwriting collaboration
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Vocal Sessions -->
        <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="service-icon">🎙️</div>
          <h3>Vocal Sessions</h3>
          <p>High-end vocal tracking in a professionally treated environment. Every nuance captured with pristine
            clarity.</p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20,6 9,17 4,12" />
              </svg>
              Acoustically treated live room
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20,6 9,17 4,12" />
              </svg>
              Professional-grade microphones
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20,6 9,17 4,12" />
              </svg>
              Vocal coaching & direction
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Final Master -->
        <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="service-icon">💿</div>
          <h3>Final Master</h3>
          <p>Radio-ready polish for Spotify, Apple Music, and every major platform. Your sound, perfected for the world.
          </p>
          <ul class="service-features">
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20,6 9,17 4,12" />
              </svg>
              Stereo & stem mastering
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20,6 9,17 4,12" />
              </svg>
              LUFS-optimized for streaming
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20,6 9,17 4,12" />
              </svg>
              Unlimited revisions
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       GALLERY — "THE LAB"
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section gallery" id="gallery">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="gallery-header reveal">
        <span class="section-label" style="justify-content: center;">Behind the Glass</span>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: center;">The Lab</h2>
        <p class="section-desc" style="text-align: center;">Where Pacific soul meets world-class engineering. A glimpse
          inside the sessions, backstage, and beyond.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-item reveal">
          <img src="/images/gallery-09.jpeg" alt="Live band performance at Tana Music session" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">Live Session</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <img src="/images/gallery-01.jpeg" alt="Harry Levy backstage at festival" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">Backstage Vibes</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <img src="/images/gallery-02.jpeg" alt="Harry at outdoor event" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">Festival Life</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <img src="/images/gallery-03.jpeg" alt="Harry with fellow artist" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">Creative Network</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <img src="/images/gallery-08.jpeg" alt="Guitar session at Tana Music" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">The Craft</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <img src="/images/gallery-04.jpeg" alt="Harry Levy and collaborator" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">Island Brotherhood</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <img src="/images/gallery-05.jpeg" alt="Harry Levy at outdoor festival" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">Pacific Sounds</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <img src="/images/gallery-06.jpeg" alt="Harry Levy with guest" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">Studio Connections</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <img src="/images/gallery-07.jpeg" alt="Acoustic session" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">Acoustic Sessions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <img src="/images/gallery-10.jpeg" alt="Harry Levy with J Boog" loading="lazy">
          <span class="overlay-text">Harry &amp; J Boog</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Lightbox -->
  <div class="lightbox" id="lightbox">
    <button class="lightbox-close" aria-label="Close lightbox">&times;</button>
    <img src="" alt="Gallery preview">
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       CONTACT
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section contact" id="contact">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div class="contact-info reveal">
          <span class="section-label">Get in Touch</span>
          <h2>Let's Create<br>Something <span class="accent">Legendary</span>.</h2>
          <p>Ready to take your sound to the next level? Whether you're an emerging artist or a seasoned performer, Tana
            Music has the tools and the talent to bring your vision to life.</p>

          <div class="contact-details">
            <div class="contact-detail">
              <div class="icon">📍</div>
              <div class="text">
                <span>Location</span>
                <p>Nadi Back Road, Fiji Islands</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-detail">
              <div class="icon">📧</div>
              <div class="text">
                <span>Email</span>
                <p>tanamusicfiji@gmail.com </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-detail">
              <div class="icon">📱</div>
              <div class="text">
                <span>Phone</span>
                <p>+679 763 2291</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-detail">
              <div class="icon">
                <div class="audio-bars">
                  <div class="bar"></div>
                  <div class="bar"></div>
                  <div class="bar"></div>
                  <div class="bar"></div>
                  <div class="bar"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text">
                <span>Status</span>
                <p style="color: #22c55e;">Currently Accepting Sessions</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-form reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <% if (success) { %>
            <div class="form-success">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14" />
                <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01" />
              </svg>
              <%= success %>
            </div>
            <% } %>
              <form action="/contact" method="POST">
                <div class="form-row">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="contact-name">Your Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" placeholder="e.g. Jope Serevi" required>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="contact-email">Email Address</label>
                    <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="email" placeholder="you@email.com" required>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="contact-service">Service Needed</label>
                  <select id="contact-service" name="service" required>
                    <option value="" disabled selected>Select a service...</option>
                    <option value="production">Full Production</option>
                    <option value="vocals">Vocal Sessions</option>
                    <option value="mastering">Final Mastering</option>
                    <option value="mixing">Mixing</option>
                    <option value="other">Other / Custom Package</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="contact-message">Your Message</label>
                  <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" rows="5"
                    placeholder="Tell us about your project, vision, and timeline..." required></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">
                  <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13" />
                    <polygon points="22,2 15,22 11,13 2,9" />
                  </svg>
                  Send Message
                </button>
              </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       FOOTER
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-top">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <img src="/images/tana-logo.jpeg" alt="Tana Music Logo">
          <div class="footer-brand-text">
            <h3>TANA MUSIC</h3>
            <p>Premium Island Studio — Fiji</p>
          </div>
        </div>
